  \section install Install

  \subsection linux Linux
  Pre-requirements: cmake armadillo blas lapack boost

  Compile: 
  \code
   mkdir build
   cd build
   cmake ..
   make
   cpack .
   dpkg -i or tar xvzf 
  \endcode


